529
00:51:11,849 --> 00:51:13,517
Ya, saya rasa itu James.

530
00:51:46,601 --> 00:51:48,651
Kami memberi dia
ubat penahan sakit, jadi dia akan baik-baik saja.

531
00:51:49,108 --> 00:51:49,795
Okay.

